# YouTube Reply Service API Testing
# Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Subscription Plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/plans

### Get AI Settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update AI Settings
PUT {{baseUrl}}/ai/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isEnabled": true,
  "replyTone": "friendly",
  "replyLength": "medium",
  "personalityTraits": {
    "enthusiasmLevel": 8,
    "formalityLevel": 5,
    "humorLevel": 6,
    "helpfulnessLevel": 9
  },
  "customInstructions": "Be helpful and engaging with viewers"
}

### Generate AI Reply (Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/generate-reply
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": {
    "id": "test-comment-123",
    "text": "Great tutorial! How did you learn to code so well?",
    "author": "Coding Newbie",
    "likeCount": 5
  },
  "videoId": "test-video-123",
  "channelId": "test-channel-123",
  "options": {
    "forceRegenerate": false,
    "saveToLog": true
  }
}

### Test AI Reply
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/test-reply
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": {
    "text": "This is amazing! Can you make a tutorial on advanced topics?",
    "author": "Test User"
  }
}

### Extract Video Transcript
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/transcripts/extract
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "channelId": "test-channel"
}

### Get AI Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get YouTube Auth URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/youtube/auth-url
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Connected Channels
GET {{baseUrl}}/youtube/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Reply Templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/youtube/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create Reply Template
POST {{baseUrl}}/youtube/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Welcome Template",
  "content": "Welcome to my channel {{username}}! Thanks for watching! ðŸŽ‰",
  "triggers": ["welcome", "new viewer", "first time"],
  "conditions": {
    "sentiment": "positive"
  },
  "isActive": true,
  "variables": [
    {
      "name": "username",
      "defaultValue": "there",
      "required": false
    }
  ]
}

### Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get User Usage
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/usage
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}